<Base
  title="Dayroll — one tap, one line a day"
  description="Dayroll is the journal you never have to open. Log your day from a widget with one tap, one line."
>
  <h1>Dayroll</h1>
  <p class="tagline">The journal you never have to open — one tap, one line a day.</p>

  <ul class="features">
    <li><strong>Log from your Home or Lock Screen</strong>
        <span>Tap the widget to mark the moment, add one line when you feel like it.</span></li>
    <li><strong>Private by design</strong>
        <span>No account, no ads, no tracking. Your entries live on your device and your iCloud.</span></li>
  </ul>

  <span class="badge">Coming soon to the App Store</span>

  <footer>
    <a href="/dayroll/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a> · <a href="/dayroll/support/">Support</a>
  </footer>
</Base>
